---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="赞助 - Josephine's Blog">
  <section class="max-w-xl">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-2">赞助支持</h1>
    <p class="text-dim text-sm mb-8">如果我的内容对你有帮助</p>

    <div class="card-minimal p-8 text-center mb-8">
      <span class="i-lucide-heart text-4xl text-red-500 mb-4 block"></span>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium mb-4">感谢你的支持！</h2>
      <p class="text-dim text-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
        你的支持是我持续创作的动力。无论是一杯咖啡 ☕ 还是一顿午餐 🍜，都将帮助我更好地维护这个博客。
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <a href="https://afdian.net" target="_blank" class="link-card justify-center">
          <span>爱发电</span>
          <span class="i-lucide-external-link text-sm opacity-40"></span>
        </a>
        <a href="https://ko-fi.com" target="_blank" class="link-card justify-center">
          <span>Ko-fi</span>
          <span class="i-lucide-external-link text-sm opacity-40"></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-dimmer text-sm">
      💌 或者你也可以通过 <a href="/contact" class="border-b border-dashed border-gray-600 hover:border-gray-400 transition-colors">联系我</a> 页面给我留言
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
